{"tid":2147913,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【灣區風情】駱主任不能滙錢美國 - 程凱","createTime":"2020-08-09T14:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T14:52:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2533d0a489245a1d4b3bb6b6de62b0fb066e0b","tid":2147913,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200809/APSTUZJP5FESRII5TXEEDAXDOA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200809%2FAPSTUZJP5FESRII5TXEEDAXDOA%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=852751fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200809%2FAPSTUZJP5FESRII5TXEEDAXDOA%2F&h=bf8f21dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200809/APSTUZJP5FESRII5TXEEDAXDOA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【灣區風情】駱主任不能滙錢美國 - 程凱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ibJYKkko7Z52r00ePep6yMDSZV4=/6385x4284/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DRWXOCY3LVGF7NJKQQQSZDQD3E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FibJYKkko7Z52r00ePep6yMDSZV4%3D%2F6385x4284%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDRWXOCY3LVGF7NJKQQQSZDQD3E.jpg&h=2f4b2f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■駱惠寧可能讀得四書五經多，中國人的文化修養特別濃厚，以為特朗普收到這100美元，就會像《三國演義》裏的周瑜般吐血而死。<br />\n<br />\n中國和美國由貿易戰開始惡鬥至今，如果用一場拳賽來作比喻，中方可說是已經被美方完全壓制到繩角，左勾拳、右勾拳不斷重擊，毫無還擊之力。站在人道立場，拳證理應結束這場賽事，因為強弱已太過懸殊，沒有再打下去的意義。<br />\n<br />\n可是，中國人都具備孔乙己「竊書不能算偷」的堅毅，...............<br />\n<br />\n就算正在被人吊打，孔乙己大概仍會辯駁稱，人家也只是看看你美帝的知識產權，左抄右抄，佔佔便宜，人權就自古以來都沒有；稍稍打壓一下香港而已，為何如今就要耍無賴，瘋狂打壓我大國崛起？中國人的事，能算偷麼？<br />\n<br />\n現實的駱主任（年初才接掌中聯辦主任一職的駱惠寧）就更霸氣了，................<br />\n<br />\n.....................就會像《三國演義》裏的周瑜般吐血而死。<br />\n<br />\n現實一點看，在美國制裁之下，駱主任已不能持有美元戶口，銀行又不會跟他提供兌換美元服務；就算讓他幸運地在街上執到一張百元美鈔，亦不會有銀行願意幫駱主任滙錢到美國，郵政和速遞公司一樣會拒絕他的郵遞請求。<br />\n<br />\n打嘴炮這回事，中國人認第一，沒有人敢爭第二。...................................<br />\n<br />\n很快，被制裁的中港官員，他們的銀行戶口、信用卡會被注銷，有貸款被即Call Loan，名下關連企業被封殺，facebook藍剔賬號被關閉；就連特區政府要出糧給林鄭月娥都十分困難，可能每月真的要提取40萬港元現鈔，再找警察押送到禮賓府上了。<br />\n<br />\n程凱<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/chengkaibayarea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fchengkaibayarea&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminBZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=b07274a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/chengkaibayarea</a>"},{"pid":"2f38620df957bc3a7eabea803318214244a4eaa0","tid":2147913,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dab10c28d3cee528b0092c2e3c564a0ce11218f","tid":2147913,"uid":74361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"走數USD100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1370ce6d41994eec9ac98081c3f87d816c867106","tid":2147913,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"仲賴得戚話寄支票去美國，其實唔可以寄。"},{"pid":"254df41d9f57518749e0a9828219f469d846cf47","tid":2147913,"uid":281437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:52:06.000Z","msg":"消滅奶共狗"}]}